      <title>Hexo-Next-Mist主题透明化以及背景图片的更改</title>
      <link href="2021/05/08/Hexo-Next-Mist%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E5%8C%96%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9/"/>
      <url>2021/05/08/Hexo-Next-Mist%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E5%8C%96%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.在 <code>hexo/themes/ next/source/css/  _ custom</code>下无<code> _custom.styl</code> 文件，自己添加 <code>_custom.styl</code>编辑后，不能实现背景图片自定义；2.找到主题配置文件 <code> _config.yml</code>并打开，按住 <code>ctrl + f</code>搜索 <code>custom_file_path:</code>把<code>style: source/_data/ _styles.styl</code>注释取消掉， 但<code>source</code>文件下无<code>_data/styles.styl</code>文件，自己添加文件编辑后，也不能实现背景图片自定义。两种情况都不能解决时，可看本文。<span id="more"></span></p><h3 id="问题描述"><a href="#问题描述" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h3><p>我前期博客的搭建按照大佬教程 <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/106060640">个人博客第8篇——优化主题（持续更新） - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a> 进行。板娘按照教程 <a href="https://lin_daren.gitee.io/lindada-blog/2020/06/19/%E7%BB%88%E4%BA%8E%E7%AD%89%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%A0%EF%BC%81%E4%B8%8D%E8%92%9C%E5%AD%90-%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%92%8C%E8%90%8C%E8%90%8C%E5%93%92-2D%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/">终于等到你！不蒜子-统计工具和萌萌哒-2D模型~ | 大大的小屋 (gitee.io)</a> 。</p><p>对于hexo-next-mist 主题的背景图片修改，当以下两种情况都不能解决时，当然我都遇到了，呜呜~。</p><p>​        1.在 <strong>hexo/themes/ \next\source\css\ _custom</strong>下无**_custom.styl** 文件，自己添加**_custom.styl**编辑后，不能实现背景图片自定义。</p><p>​        2.找到主题配置文件 <strong>_config.yml</strong> 并打开，按住 <strong>ctrl + f</strong> 搜索 <strong>custom_file_path:</strong> 把 <strong>style: source/_data/ _styles.styl</strong> 注释取消掉， 但<strong>source</strong>文件下无**_data/styles.styl**文件，自己添加文件编辑后，仍不能实现背景图片自定义</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">custom_file_path:</span><br><span class="line">  #head: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;head.swig</span><br><span class="line">  #header: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;header.swig</span><br><span class="line">  #sidebar: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;sidebar.swig</span><br><span class="line">  #postMeta: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;post-meta.swig</span><br><span class="line">  #postBodyEnd: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;post-body-end.swig</span><br><span class="line">  #footer: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;footer.swig</span><br><span class="line">  #bodyEnd: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;body-end.swig</span><br><span class="line">  #variable: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;variables.styl</span><br><span class="line">  #mixin: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;mixins.styl</span><br><span class="line">  style: source&#x2F;_data&#x2F;styles.styl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="问题解决"><a href="#问题解决" class="headerlink" title="问题解决"></a>问题解决</h3><h4 id="更改博客背景"><a href="#更改博客背景" class="headerlink" title="更改博客背景"></a>更改博客背景</h4><p>打开文件<strong>themes/next/source/css/_schemes/Mist/ _layout.styl</strong>文件，在末尾添加如下代码</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">body &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        background-image: url(&#39;..&#x2F;images&#x2F;background.jpg&#39;); </span><br><span class="line">        background-repeat: no-repeat;</span><br><span class="line">        background-attachment: fixed;</span><br><span class="line">        background-position: 50% 50%;</span><br><span class="line">        background-size: 100% 100%;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="代码解释"><a href="#代码解释" class="headerlink" title="代码解释"></a>代码解释</h5><ul><li>background:url为图片路径，将图片重命名为<strong>background.jpg</strong>放在\themes\next\source\images下，当然也可以直接使用链接，图片上传至图床，生成url，（好用免费图床： <a href="https://sm.ms/">Image Upload - SM.MS - Simple Free Image Hosting</a>） 。</li><li>background-repeat：若果背景图片不能全屏，那么是否平铺显示，充满屏幕</li><li>background-attachment：背景是否随着网页上下滚动而滚动，fixed为固定</li><li>background-position：就是调整图片的位置</li><li>background-size：图片展示大小，这里设置100% 100%的意义为：如果背景图片不能全屏，那么是否通过拉伸的方式将背景强制拉伸至全屏显示。</li></ul><h4 id="更改菜单栏背景及透明度"><a href="#更改菜单栏背景及透明度" class="headerlink" title="更改菜单栏背景及透明度"></a>更改菜单栏背景及透明度</h4><p>打开文件<strong>themes/next/source/css/_schemes/Mist/ _header.styl</strong>文件，在如下所示位置修改代码：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; Header</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; --------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">.header &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;&#x2F;background: var(--content-bg-color); </span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;&#x2F;上一行代码修改成下一行代码</span><br><span class="line">  background: url(&#39;..&#x2F;images&#x2F;header.jpg&#39;);  </span><br><span class="line">  opacity: 0.7; &#x2F;&#x2F;添加的代码，更改透明度</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.header-inner &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  align-items: center;</span><br><span class="line">  display: flex;</span><br><span class="line">  padding: 20px 0;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  +mobile() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    display: block;</span><br><span class="line">    padding: 10px 0;</span><br><span class="line">    width: auto;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="代码解释-1"><a href="#代码解释-1" class="headerlink" title="代码解释"></a>代码解释</h5><ul><li>图片（好用免费图库： <a href="https://wallhaven.cc/">Awesome Wallpapers - wallhaven.cc</a>） 重命名为<strong>header.jpg</strong>放在\themes\next\source\images下，当然也可以直接使用url链接。</li></ul><h4 id="更改底栏背景"><a href="#更改底栏背景" class="headerlink" title="更改底栏背景"></a>更改底栏背景</h4><p>打开文件<strong>themes/next/source/css/_schemes/Mist/ _layout.styl</strong>文件，按 <strong>ctrl + f</strong> 搜索 <strong>.footer</strong>，修改如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.footer &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;&#x2F;background: var(--content-bg-color);</span><br><span class="line">  &#x2F;&#x2F;上一行代码修改成下一行代码</span><br><span class="line">  background: url(&#39;..&#x2F;images&#x2F;footer.jpg&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">  opacity: 0.7; &#x2F;&#x2F;添加的代码，更改透明度</span><br><span class="line">  color: var(--text-color);</span><br><span class="line">  padding: 10px 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="代码解释-2"><a href="#代码解释-2" class="headerlink" title="代码解释"></a>代码解释</h5><ul><li>图片重命名为<strong>footer.jpg</strong>放在\themes\next\source\images下，当然也可以直接使用url链接。</li></ul><h4 id="更改站点概况背景"><a href="#更改站点概况背景" class="headerlink" title="更改站点概况背景"></a>更改站点概况背景</h4><p>打开<strong>themes/next/source/css/_schemes/Must/ _sidebar.styl</strong>，按 <strong>ctrl + f</strong> 搜索 <strong>the-transition-ease-out</strong>，添加代码<code>background: url(&#39;../images/sidebar.jpg&#39;);</code>位置如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.sidebar &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  width: $sidebar-desktop;</span><br><span class="line">  z-index: $zindex-2;</span><br><span class="line">  the-transition-ease-out();</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  background: url(&#39;..&#x2F;images&#x2F;sidebar.jpg&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  a, span.exturl &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    border-bottom-color: $black-light;</span><br><span class="line">    color: $grey-dark;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &amp;:hover &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      border-bottom-color: $gainsboro;</span><br><span class="line">      color: $gainsboro;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="代码解释-3"><a href="#代码解释-3" class="headerlink" title="代码解释"></a>代码解释</h5><ul><li>图片重命名为<strong>sidebar.jpg</strong>放在\themes\next\source\images下，当然也可以直接使用url链接。</li><li>文件路径是在<strong>Must</strong>主题下，不用奇怪，因为<strong>themes/next/source/css/_schemes/Mist/__index.styl</strong>文件中有<code>@import &#39;../Muse/_sidebar&#39;;</code>这一行代码，表明主题<strong>Mist</strong>的<strong>sidebar</strong>的配置在Muse主题下修改。</li></ul><h4 id="内容板块透明"><a href="#内容板块透明" class="headerlink" title="内容板块透明"></a>内容板块透明</h4><p>打开<strong>themes/next/source/css/_schemes/Mist/ _layout.styl</strong>，按 <strong>ctrl + f</strong> 搜索 <strong>.content</strong>，添加代码<code>background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);</code>位置如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.content &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  padding-top: 80px;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); &#x2F;&#x2F;0.5是透明度</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  +mobile() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    padding-top: 60px;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="效果图"><a href="#效果图" class="headerlink" title="效果图"></a>效果图</h3><h4 id="博客背景、菜单栏背景、站点概况背景、内容板块透明"><a href="#博客背景、菜单栏背景、站点概况背景、内容板块透明" class="headerlink" title="博客背景、菜单栏背景、站点概况背景、内容板块透明"></a>博客背景、菜单栏背景、站点概况背景、内容板块透明</h4><p><img src="/2021/05/08/Hexo-Next-Mist%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E5%8C%96%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9/%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF.png"></p><h4 id="底栏背景"><a href="#底栏背景" class="headerlink" title="底栏背景"></a>底栏背景</h4><p><img src="/2021/05/08/Hexo-Next-Mist%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E5%8C%96%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9/%E5%BA%95%E6%A0%8F%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF.png"></p><h3 id="参考链接："><a href="#参考链接：" class="headerlink" title="参考链接："></a>参考链接：</h3><p> <a href="https://www.wolfdan.cn/Hexo-Next-Gemini%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E5%8C%96%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9/">Hexo-Next-Gemini主题透明化以及背景图片的更改和获取 | 单林敏的博客 (wolfdan.cn)</a> </p><p> <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_40837922/article/details/88047241">(2条消息) 给hexo主题添加背景及更改字体颜色（next的Mist主题）_姜姜酱的博客-CSDN博客</a> </p><p> <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/c8de95fae5f5">Hexo-Next-Mist主题头部顶栏背景图片设置 - 简书 (jianshu.com)</a> </p>]]></content>
      
      
